<div style="clear:both;">
      <p>PillowCheck is a reservation management software system designed 
					for the needs of the smaller hospitality property. Pillowcheck is available free of charge for property managers with 10 rental units or less.</p>
				  <p>Manage your<b> Hotel</b>, <b>Motel </b>or <b>B&amp;B</b> 
					easily and efficiently using the flexible, powerful and easy 
					to use PillowCheck reservation management software system.</p>
				  <p>Whether you are managing a dsingle rental property or have an inventory of  100+ rooms, PillowCheck can help 
					you manage your property efficiently and profitably. PillowCheck 
					provides tools to manage your property, from reservation screens, 
					to room and rate categorization and management, to month end 
					and year end reporting. </p>
